<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1183284-could-this-book-be-considered-science">Could this book be considered Science fiction?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1183284'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F13438524-flight-behavior">like</a></span>

